    - **BREAK-SPIN merge (`operator_break_spin`):** When the Layer 0 hand-off includes **`## operator_break_spin`** with a fenced **`yaml`** block and **`operator_break_spin: true`** (parse after the base Next-Need Resolver + gate merge, **before** serializing **`layer1_resolver_hints`**):
