      - Build **`break_spin_context`**: **`circled_locus`** (from YAML or best-effort current target string, else `unknown`), **`suggested_deepen_targets`** (string array — best-effort sibling / under-touched phase paths from **`workflow_state.md`** / phase roadmap when resolvable for **`project_id`**; **may be empty**), **`alternate_available`**: `suggested_deepen_targets.length > 0`.
      - **Merge** into the resolver record used for **`layer1_resolver_hints`**: set **`operator_break_spin: true`**, **`break_spin_context`**. When **`alternate_available`** and Second-Brain-Config **`queue.break_spin_prefer_alternate_deepen`** is not **false** (default **true**): set **`effective_action`** to **`deepen`** unless **`break_spin_preferred_action`** is set to a concrete allowed roadmap action; set **`effective_target`** to the first **`suggested_deepen_targets`** entry not equal to **`circled_locus`** when possible, else first entry. When **`not alternate_available`**: if **`queue.break_spin_recal_fallback_when_no_alternate`** is **true** (default), set **`effective_action: recal`** as **fallback** only; else set **`no_gain_signal: true`** (Layer 2 emits terminal **`queue_continuation`** with **`suppress_reason: no_gain_pending_user_gates`**, neutral prose). When **`break_spin_rationale`** is non-empty, append it to the roadmap **`Task`** hand-off **`params.user_guidance`** (or hand-off **`prompt`**) for this entry.
